\f0\b\fs40 \cf0 \ulnone Computation of H3
\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
The most expensive step in sampling is the computation of H3. There are two practical ways to compute H3: using the FFT (with a plan!) or using the recursive formula (REC).\
\
